# State Machine Rules

- Code: `features/shared/state-machines/`
- Runner: `lib/core/transition-runner.ts`
- Docs: `docs/architecture/state-machine.md`

禁止:
- `campaign.status = "APPROVED"`
- `if (status === "REVIEWING")` 作为业务分支（UI 展示除外）

必须:
- `campaignService.transition(id, event, actor)`
- 非法转换返回 409 INVALID_STATE_TRANSITION
